{"tid":249161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"DSE連續兩年加價     明年考六科要$2,894","createTime":"2017-05-19T06:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T19:29:42.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5ce77cb7eaec21ed5f88050191fd9bb05f3a4e24","tid":249161,"uid":48093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T06:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495173731_86d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495173731_86d7.jpg&h=c9b8366f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港考試及評核局連續兩年加中學文憑試考試費，今日在憲報刊憲公佈，2018年的中學文憑試加考試費，加幅約4%。明年自修生報名費為475元，較今年增加18元，加幅3.39%。明年語文科考試費為619元，較今年增加24元，加幅4%。明年其他科目414元，較今增加16元，增幅4%。以明年報考兩語文及4個非語文計算，考生需付2,894元，較今年增加約4%。<br />\n<br />\n考評局於去年亦有調整2017年考試費，當時增幅約3%。"},{"pid":"4912e0f6dfc4ad76c8a197e8d13249447465a498","tid":249161,"uid":15815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"貼錢買難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81d6390d2d55cfc745ac25794062941cbc72ff6e","tid":249161,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n呢啲必須品就應該免費啦<br />\n<br />\n政府正仆街"},{"pid":"fc3996d11dcc4140699f6be41881514289b8dea1","tid":249161,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T07:50:14.000Z","msg":"又加價，正hi hi"},{"pid":"8630f1783cf8e67498544142ee3e064f3e15f9a1","tid":249161,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>貼錢買難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係都要比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40aa8fe9d467133f3e09ac8fb87c91340db3c3d6","tid":249161,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0